HEADWORD: Railing
<hw>Rail"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Expressing reproach;
insulting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Angels, which are greater in power and might, bring not
<qex>railing</qex> accusation against them.</q> <rj><qau>2 Pet. ii.
11.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
